array.string: FEAR LEADS TO HATE, HATE LEADS TO ANGER, ANGER LEADS TO DARKSIDE, DARKSIDE LEADS TO MARK, RYAN AND AJ.
I THINK WE CONSIDER TOO MUCH THE GOOD LUCK OF THE EARLY BIRD AND NOT ENOUGH THE BAD LUCK OF THE EARLY WORM.
IF ONLY WE'D STOP TRYING TO BE HAPPY, WE'D HAVE A PRETTY GOOD TIME.
LIFE IS PLEASANT. DEATH IS PEACEFUL. IT'S THE TRANSITION THAT'S TROUBLESOME.
THERE ARE NEVER TEN WAYS TO DO SOMETHING, ONLY ONE. THAT IS A QUESTION ON MORALITY.
ONE OF THE PLEASURES OF READING OLD LETTERS IS THE KNOWLEDGE THAT THEY NEED NO ANSWER.
IF WOMEN DIDN'T EXIST, ALL THE MONEY IN THE WORLD WOULD HAVE NO MEANING.
WE ALL LONG FOR LOVE. WHETHER WE KNOW IT OR NOT, EVERYTHING ELSE WE DO IS JUST KILLING TIME.
EVEN IN ONE'S OWN AREA OF EXPERTISE, THE LONGER YOU STUDY AND SPECIALIZE, THE MORE YOU KNOW ABOUT LESS AND LESS.
THE REVOLUTION IS NOT AN APPLE THAT FALLS WHEN IT IS RIPE. YOU HAVE TO MAKE IT FALL.
ONLY A LIFE LIVED FOR OTHERS IS A LIFE WORTHWHILE.
